304
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:39,330
There's an exclusive mark on it for you.

305
00:12:39,420 --> 00:12:40,800
They call you Hua.

306
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:42,560
So I carve a sunflower for you,

307
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:43,810
which means sun

308
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:44,810
and warmth.

309
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,500
So

310
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,840
I'll take you to school tomorrow.

311
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:53,320
Take this to school?

312
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:54,960
It's too stupid.

313
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,640
You think it's lame, huh?

314
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:03,350
Well, I'll go back and improve it.

315
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:13,240
Actually

316
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:15,990
it's kind of cute.

317
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:22,880
Do you like it?

318
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,920
Since you've carved the flower on it,

319
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:26,350
