320
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:27,730
Okay.

321
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:30,000
I'll put it in the shed later.

322
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,150
It's so cold. Let's go back.

323
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:36,960
Let me help you.

324
00:14:05,380 --> 00:14:06,330
You just practice.

325
