326
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:09,640
I'm not practising today.

327
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:17,600
Come down.

328
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:28,250
So...

329
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:29,600
So we'll continue to practice tomorrow.

330
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,140
Okay.

331
00:14:32,370 --> 00:14:33,600
I'm going to go.

332
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:37,800
Li Qing Tong.

333
00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:41,280
Are you

334
00:14:41,370 --> 00:14:42,520
hungry?

335
00:14:45,890 --> 00:14:46,870
Yeah.

336
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:53,120
You have to go home.

337
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:54,210
Okay.

338
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,180
Bye-bye.

339
00:14:59,140 --> 00:15:00,120
See you tomorrow.

340
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:01,880
See you every day.

341
00:15:11,770 --> 00:15:13,380
[Trust wins the world]

342
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:15,590
Tell you what. Eating
meat must eat streaky pork.

343
00:15:16,050 --> 00:15:17,790
It won't taste good if
you just eat the lean part.

344
00:15:18,010 --> 00:15:19,050
Look at this little fat.

345
00:15:19,130 --> 00:15:20,550
There is still grease on it.

346
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:22,160
Dip it in chilli.

347
00:15:24,610 --> 00:15:26,520
At the same time, take a sip of soda.

348
00:15:30,770 --> 00:15:32,080
Oh, my God.

349
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:39,760
You try a sip of soda.

350
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,960
I don't drink soda.

351
00:15:45,410 --> 00:15:47,810
What's the point of eating
if you don't drink soda?

352
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:49,800
Why do we need a point when we eat?

353
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:53,430
Eating time is the
happiest time of our life.

354
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:55,160
My dad says that

355
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:56,770
