357
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:02,170
Eating and sleeping are
the biggest parts of a human's life.

358
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:03,720
Having a good meal is a blessing.

359
00:16:05,300 --> 00:16:06,180
OK.

360
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:23,640
Am I eating too much?

361
00:16:25,740 --> 00:16:27,280
This dinner is on me.

362
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:29,560
