389
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,150
Think of it as the fare.

390
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:56,970
That's ok.

391
00:17:57,060 --> 00:17:57,940
Thank you, boss.

392
00:17:58,140 --> 00:17:59,490
