396
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:05,150
Let's go.

397
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:08,990
This little sled is cute.

398
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:10,470
Let's go.

399
00:18:11,180 --> 00:18:12,150
Let's go.

400
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,500
Come on.

401
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:21,140
[Year One Class One study group roster]

402
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:23,030
Who hasn't teamed up yet?

403
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:24,120
