408
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:36,560
Yeah, the monitor only wants
to team up with Wu Zhi Xun.

409
00:18:38,340 --> 00:18:39,760
What are you talking about, Wang Xiao Min?

410
00:18:40,860 --> 00:18:41,950
Don't talk nonsense.

411
00:18:42,940 --> 00:18:43,790
You tell Wu that

412
00:18:43,870 --> 00:18:45,490
