423
00:19:26,620 --> 00:19:29,470
[Li Qing Tong]

424
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,490
Let me know next time.

425
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:42,800
You stand up suddenly. It scares me.

426
00:19:51,310 --> 00:19:58,080
[Wu Zhi Xun, Li Qing Tong]

427
00:20:13,860 --> 00:20:14,740
Qing Tong.

428
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,060
Qing Tong.

429
00:20:16,170 --> 00:20:17,480
Give the water to Wu Zhi Xun.

430
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:23,650
He sits there alone.

431
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:25,370
