encouragement. Do you understand?

433
00:20:27,780 --> 00:20:28,760
Go, go.

434
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:37,890
Wu Zhi Xun.

435
00:20:37,970 --> 00:20:39,390
Would you like some water?

436
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,040
Darn it.

437
00:20:48,060 --> 00:20:49,240
She is shameless.

438
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:55,790
Da Mao, I find that

439
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:58,640
I'm better at one-on-one games.

440
00:20:59,020 --> 00:20:59,960
To tell you the truth,

441
00:21:00,380 --> 00:21:01,360
in our school,

442
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,920
