487
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:39,160
Okay.

488
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:42,880
Are you ready?

489
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:46,940
Let's go.

490
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:49,990
Come on, Wu Zhi Xun.

491
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:58,250
The rule is

492
00:22:58,340 --> 00:23:00,010
