493
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:00,930
OK

494
00:23:01,010 --> 00:23:01,890
OK.

495
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:05,780
You first.

496
00:23:34,570 --> 00:23:35,450
One to zero.

497
00:23:58,650 --> 00:23:59,530
Well done.

498
00:24:00,290 --> 00:24:01,190
One to one.

499
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:09,390
Two to one.

500
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:20,400
I know Duan Xiao.

501
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:21,790
