502
00:24:21,870 --> 00:24:23,290
So you just try to let
him make a long shot.

503
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,070
Say some provocative
words at the same time.

504
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:31,390
He's a veteran.

505
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,490
You're a rookie.

506
00:24:32,580 --> 00:24:33,810
If he feels losing face,

507
00:24:33,900 --> 00:24:34,920
you'll have the chance.

508
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:36,490
What?

509
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,560
