510
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:10,710
Two to two.

511
00:25:36,300 --> 00:25:37,320
Three to two.

512
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,160
Wu Zhi Xun wins.

513
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,250
I can't do this.

514
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:43,760
I'm just not interested.

515
00:25:44,930 --> 00:25:45,600
What is it?

516
00:25:45,690 --> 00:25:46,730
It is an affectation.

517
00:25:46,810 --> 00:25:47,890
I'm speechless.

518
00:25:47,980 --> 00:25:48,790
Xiao.

519
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,090
You tell me the truth.

520
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,130
Did you let him win?

521
00:25:51,210 --> 00:25:52,570
