522
00:25:52,650 --> 00:25:53,880
I just didn't win.

523
00:25:58,520 --> 00:25:59,400
Bro.

524
00:25:59,860 --> 00:26:02,240
Why is it so easy for us
to win the championship?

525
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,570
Unlike someone,

526
00:26:03,650 --> 00:26:05,930
