lead in the semi-finals.

530
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:12,490
There is no need to show off.

531
00:26:12,580 --> 00:26:14,320
There's always next time, you know.

532
00:26:14,410 --> 00:26:16,000
Leave him alone.

533
00:26:18,260 --> 00:26:19,370
I hear

534
