I can only count on you.

574
00:27:56,020 --> 00:27:57,360
Only you can help me.

575
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:00,050
Okay.

576
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:01,280
I'll help you.

577
00:28:06,460 --> 00:28:08,490
In fact, he is really good.

578
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:10,290
I thought he knew
nothing about basketball.

579
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,570
I'm worried about how to act.

580
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:13,810
But I was stunned by that layup.

581
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:15,350
And he bumped against me badly.

582
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,570
Wu Zhi Xun

583
00:28:17,650 --> 00:28:20,280
is a guy who pursues
perfection in everything.

584
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:21,690
Since he started practising,

585
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:23,330
he works for four hours a day.

586
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:24,410
I am stunned.

587
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:26,350
That is why he is the first
in the exam all the time.

588
00:28:26,670 --> 00:28:27,780
You do well, too.

589
00:28:27,870 --> 00:28:28,880
Your acting is perfect.

590
00:28:28,970 --> 00:28:29,970
You could be an actor.

591
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:31,240
It's all your fault.

592
00:28:31,580 --> 00:28:33,030
As the Basketball God of our school,

593
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,680
my reputation has been ruined.

594
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:36,200
Never mind.

595
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:38,110
It doesn't matter if others
don't recognize you.

596
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,720
You'll always be the
only Basketball God in my heart.

597
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:44,410
So...

598
00:28:44,490 --> 00:28:45,440
So

599
00:28:46,370 --> 00:28:48,040
I'll be your god.

600
00:28:57,620 --> 00:28:58,680
Where's Mrs Peony?

601
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:00,290
She's upstairs.

602
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:01,840
I'll check on her.

603
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:05,300
Mum.

604
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,510
Hua comes.

605
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:22,720
Hua.

606
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:26,000
Why aren't you guys sleeping yet?

607
00:29:26,820 --> 00:29:29,590
Tomorrow we will sit
according to our study groups.

608
00:29:30,250 --> 00:29:32,350
I'm about to sit next to Wu Zhi Xun.

609
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:35,840
I'm too nervous to sleep right now.

610
00:29:36,140 --> 00:29:38,070
Idiot.

611
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:42,030
He is so strict in daily life.

612
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:43,970
Will he always scold me

613
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:45,400
because I can't learn well?

614
00:29:47,330 --> 00:29:49,010
If he dares to scold you, you tell me.

615
00:29:49,090 --> 00:29:50,950
Only I can scold you.
No one else can do that.

616
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,200
Well, that's not exactly true.

617
00:29:54,620 --> 00:29:55,880
If he scolds me,

618
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:57,840
that's okay.

619
00:29:58,770 --> 00:30:00,840
Can you have a conscience?

620
00:30:05,250 --> 00:30:06,790
Hua.

621
00:30:09,370 --> 00:30:11,560
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

622
00:30:22,780 --> 00:30:23,650
Our teacher said that

623
00:30:23,730 --> 00:30:24,520
from now on,

624
00:30:24,610 --> 00:30:26,530
everyone will be seated
according to one-to-one groups.

625
00:30:26,610 --> 00:30:27,800
Here we go.

626
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,140
Tong.

627
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:35,630
Don't go.

628
00:30:37,050 --> 00:30:38,240
I'll come back to see you.

629
00:30:50,130 --> 00:30:51,200
Hi, monitor.

630
00:31:08,980 --> 00:31:09,850
Tong.

631
00:31:12,580 --> 00:31:13,810
Two little gifts for you.

632
00:31:13,900 --> 00:31:15,320
What else would you like to eat?

633
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:17,530
I wonder why you are in
such a hurry this morning.

634
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:18,680
You are in a hurry to change your seat.

635
00:31:20,780 --> 00:31:22,000
I am the unluckiest person.

636
00:31:22,370 --> 00:31:23,710
I'm the unlucky one.

637
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:26,840
You sit there.

638
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,280
What should we do?

639
00:31:44,370 --> 00:31:45,770
Just sit here?

640
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:46,790
Just sit here.

641
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:49,760
Anyway, I suggest we
don't talk much in the future.

642
00:31:50,210 --> 00:31:51,630
Be quiet and be ourselves.

643
00:31:55,490 --> 00:31:56,370
Where are you going?

644
00:31:56,460 --> 00:31:57,800
I want someone to change seats with me.

645
00:31:58,680 --> 00:31:59,560
Come back.

646
00:32:00,940 --> 00:32:01,960
Sit down first.

647
00:32:06,540 --> 00:32:09,040
If you change seats with others
as soon as we became deskmates,

648
00:32:09,130 --> 00:32:10,760
I will be humiliated.

649
00:32:11,770 --> 00:32:13,050
I don't care about you.

650
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,160
It's none of my business.

651
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,040
Fine.

652
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:22,550
Let's just focus on the math

653
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:23,650
seriously.

654
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:24,620
Come on.

655
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:32,760
Y equals to A plus B.

656
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:44,400
Do you know how to do this?

657
00:32:51,290 --> 00:32:53,030
What the hell is this?

658
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,490
In two inequalities,

659
00:33:06,570 --> 00:33:08,120
if the left side of each

660
00:33:08,210 --> 00:33:10,290
is bigger or smaller than the right side,

661
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:13,240
then the two inequalities are
inequalities in the same direction.

662
00:33:17,250 --> 00:33:18,400
Repeat that.

663
00:33:24,780 --> 00:33:26,930
Let me see which chapter it is.

664
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:28,350
I didn't catch that.

665
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:51,470
Hey.

666
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:53,310
What?

667
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:57,080
I think we need to learn from them.

668
00:33:57,170 --> 00:33:58,390
Learn what?

669
00:33:58,700 --> 00:34:01,720
The atmosphere of studying hard together.

670
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:05,280
You should memorize the formula, too.

671
00:34:08,070 --> 00:34:08,949
Okay.

672
00:34:09,139 --> 00:34:10,480
Let's make progress together.

673
00:34:14,219 --> 00:34:15,480
Look at this question.

674
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:17,360
In the first step,

675
00:34:17,699 --> 00:34:19,280
can we use this formula?

676
00:34:20,290 --> 00:34:21,170
How?

677
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:22,710
Use this formula.

678
00:34:23,139 --> 00:34:24,760
Why else would I ask
you to memorize formulas?

679
00:34:26,260 --> 00:34:28,850
Why is this formula used here?

680
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:30,480
There is no triangle.

681
00:34:36,449 --> 00:34:37,969
Make an auxiliary line here.

682
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:39,600
Is there a triangle?

683
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:42,679
Yeah.

684
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:46,170
How do you know to draw a line here?

685
00:34:46,250 --> 00:34:47,770
The question doesn't mention it.

686
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:48,920
Li Qing Tong.

687
00:34:49,449 --> 00:34:52,000
How do you get through the
math classes all these years?

688
00:34:55,219 --> 00:34:56,199
By sitting.

689
00:35:01,380 --> 00:35:02,360
I'm sorry.

690
00:35:02,530 --> 00:35:03,630
There is no "sorry",

691
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,160
but only not studying hard.

692
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:07,150
With your current basis,

693
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,910
I don't think I can do anything.

694
00:35:15,970 --> 00:35:23,360
[Mathematics]

695
00:35:23,740 --> 00:35:24,870
Be scolded.

696
00:35:30,660 --> 00:35:31,910
In three days,

697
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,170
you got yelled at three times.

698
00:35:33,260 --> 00:35:34,800
I don't know what to say about you.

699
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:37,910
I'm very serious.

700
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,120
He's too demanding.

701
00:35:40,610 --> 00:35:41,570
What do you mean?

702
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,880
Are you giving up now?

703
00:35:43,250 --> 00:35:44,280
No.

704
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:46,120
I will certainly study hard.

705
00:35:46,210 --> 00:35:47,750
I have to study hard to prove myself.

706
00:35:55,570 --> 00:35:57,000
[Monthly Mathematics Test]

707
00:35:59,900 --> 00:36:00,370
Qing Tong.

708
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:01,630
What did you get?

709
00:36:37,910 --> 00:36:39,670
[Monthly Mathematics Test]

710
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,520
I can't coach her.

711
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:43,430
She doesn't even know the basics.

712
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:45,040
She doesn't know all the formulas.

713
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:46,410
I don't understand

714
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:48,690
how she managed to get through
all these years of schooling?

715
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:51,230
That's why she only gets a nine.

716
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:53,290
Otherwise I won't ask you to help her.

717
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:54,870
I have done my best.

718
00:36:55,140 --> 00:36:56,690
If she learns seriously,

719
00:36:56,780 --> 00:36:58,290
she won't get a nine.

720
00:36:58,380 --> 00:36:59,650
I also need to study.

721
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:00,970
I don't have a lot of time for her.

722
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:02,910
Can you hold it a little longer?

723
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,770
Are you on good terms with her?

724
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,170
You just help your friend.

725
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,490
On good terms?

726
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,830
What's the relationship
between me and her?

727
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:13,410
Tell you what,

728
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:15,680
I'll help her with the basic knowledge.

729
00:37:15,770 --> 00:37:17,040
So I can lighten your load.

730
00:37:17,210 --> 00:37:18,160
Is this OK?

731
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:21,450
I'm going to give you some formulas

732
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:23,250
and points needed to memorize.

733
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:24,760
You tell her to memorize them.

734
00:37:29,850 --> 00:37:30,410
Li Qing Tong.

735
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:31,720
You get out of there.

736
00:37:35,980 --> 00:37:37,720
You insisted on proving yourself.

737
00:37:38,210 --> 00:37:40,080
With nine points?

738
00:37:41,940 --> 00:37:43,680
I had tried my best.

739
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:46,850
How do I know that I
would get a single digit?

740
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,050
If you go on like this,

741
00:37:48,130 --> 00:37:49,520
there will be no one to help you.

742
00:37:52,660 --> 00:37:54,640
I didn't ask you to help me.

743
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,620
You do this all on your own.

744
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:58,320
So it's my fault?

745
00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:02,210
But I have tried my best.

746
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:03,530
You people keep scolding me.

747
00:38:03,620 --> 00:38:05,070
Don't I have a temper?

748
00:38:05,410 --> 00:38:06,390
You get a temper.

749
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,720
Li Qing Tong, tell me.

750
00:38:07,810 --> 00:38:09,350
What kind of temper do you have?

751
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:12,540
What?

752
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:14,730
Mr Wu.

753
00:38:14,820 --> 00:38:15,250
It's all right.

754
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:17,650
I just see you guys
having a heated discussion

755
00:38:17,730 --> 00:38:19,240
and want to be a part of you.

756
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:21,120
I think the atmosphere
is particularly good.

757
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:23,430
Just the words don't have to be too fiery.

758
00:38:23,990 --> 00:38:24,770
Friends

759
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,850
push each other.

760
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:27,890
It is very effective.

761
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:29,830
That's better than
anything the teacher says.

762
00:38:30,620 --> 00:38:31,650
I regard her as a friend.

763
00:38:31,740 --> 00:38:32,970
But she treats me like
a daughter all the time.

764
00:38:33,060 --> 00:38:33,770
Who can stand it?

765
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:35,050
Say it again, Li Qing Tong.

766
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:36,310
Don't be angry.

767
00:38:37,260 --> 00:38:39,010
Study depends on diligence,

768
00:38:39,100 --> 00:38:41,160
which can not be improved in a day.

769
00:38:41,250 --> 00:38:42,810
I definitely understand your idea

770
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:43,970
of helping Li Qing Tong.

771
00:38:44,060 --> 00:38:45,920
But you should pay attention
to the ways and methods.

772
00:38:46,450 --> 00:38:48,970
We can't deny or complain about each other

773
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:50,170
when we encounter small setbacks.

774
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:51,480
Hold on.

775
00:38:52,220 --> 00:38:53,100
Come on.

776
00:38:54,250 --> 00:38:55,320
I understand, teacher.

777
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:56,840
Back to the classroom.

778
00:38:58,500 --> 00:38:59,090
Be patient.

779
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:00,070
Don't be angry.

780
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:01,820
What a good friend she is.

781
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,590
If I have this friend, I will be
admitted to Tsinghua University.

782
00:39:07,130 --> 00:39:08,010
You...

783
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:09,440
You...

784
00:39:09,530 --> 00:39:11,110
You should play this card.

785
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,650
Bystanders can't interrupt when
playing cards. Do you know?

786
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:14,280
You play your cards.

787
00:39:14,370 --> 00:39:15,320
Watch your cards.

788
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:21,600
It's burnt.

789
00:39:25,340 --> 00:39:26,840
Are you two fighting again?

790
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:30,520
Look at her.

791
00:39:31,140 --> 00:39:32,690
Her score is like submitting
a blank paper in an exam.

792
00:39:32,770 --> 00:39:34,130
but she is still in the mood for fun.

793
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,810
That's her character.

794
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:37,280
You're angry with her all the time.

795
00:39:37,370 --> 00:39:38,560
What's the point?

796
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,520
You can't bake like
that. It won't taste good.

797
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:44,290
How to bake it?

798
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:45,280
I'll do it.

799
00:39:50,340 --> 00:39:52,320
I don't think you have
to take this seriously.

800
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:55,290
Li Qing Tong is used to being free.

801
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,850
Your oppressive style of teaching

802
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,210
can only have negative effects.

803
00:39:58,290 --> 00:40:00,560
But I am doing it for her.

804
00:40:01,470 --> 00:40:02,050
To be honest,

805
00:40:02,130 --> 00:40:03,370
every time you say that,

806
00:40:03,450 --> 00:40:04,650
I feel like you're her mother.

807
00:40:04,740 --> 00:40:05,880
You are like her mother.

808
00:40:05,970 --> 00:40:07,250
It is true.

809
00:40:07,340 --> 00:40:08,650
Every time I see you.

810
00:40:08,730 --> 00:40:10,650
Nine times out of ten, you're mad at her.

811
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:11,410
You always do this.

812
00:40:11,490 --> 00:40:13,080
She must hate you.

813
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:17,040
Let us know when the meat is cooked.

814
00:40:20,290 --> 00:40:22,390
I know you mean well.

815
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:23,880
But I think

816
00:40:24,130 --> 00:40:25,360
you can't always lose your temper

817
00:40:25,450 --> 00:40:27,080
with someone you like.

818
00:40:27,450 --> 00:40:29,170
Temper is reserved for bad people.

819
00:40:29,260 --> 00:40:31,190
Courtesy is for one of your own.

820
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:34,450
Are you the one they sent to educate me?

821
00:40:34,540 --> 00:40:35,790
I am reasoning with you.

822
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:37,220
Think about it yourself.

823
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,050
We've known each other a long time.

824
00:40:39,140 --> 00:40:41,560
I've hardly ever seen you happy.

825
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:43,440
Are you sure this is a good idea?

826
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:47,640
I'd like to help Li Qing Tong with you.

827
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:50,400
But we should do it in an orderly way.

828
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:53,680
Okay.

829
00:40:53,980 --> 00:40:55,080
You are right.

830
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:56,460
OK.

831
00:40:56,930 --> 00:40:57,810
Here.

832
00:40:58,100 --> 00:40:59,000
Taste my meat.

833
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,360
No.

834
00:41:01,580 --> 00:41:02,710
The meat I toast.

835
00:41:10,740 --> 00:41:11,720
Is it tasty?

836
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:13,000
No.

837
00:41:13,090 --> 00:41:14,050
You must think it's delicious.

838
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,200
I can see that.

839
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,600
It's just not good.

840
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:18,740
What?

841
00:41:21,130 --> 00:41:22,490
Let me tell you about

842
00:41:22,570 --> 00:41:23,810
my determination to study hard.

843
00:41:23,890 --> 00:41:24,770
How?

844
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:26,400
I'll show you when you go home.

845
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:29,140
All right.

846
00:41:31,100 --> 00:41:31,980
Eat meat.

847
00:41:33,620 --> 00:41:34,330
Don't play.

848
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:35,210
Eat meat.

849
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:36,190
Here we go.

850
00:41:37,970 --> 00:41:39,640
Come on, you can play later.

851
00:41:39,780 --> 00:41:41,320
Give me the chopsticks.

852
00:41:42,690 --> 00:41:43,290
Come on, come on.

853
00:41:43,380 --> 00:41:44,350
Coming.

854
00:41:56,820 --> 00:41:58,480
What are you doing?

855
00:41:59,210 --> 00:42:00,450
Hang my head.

856
00:42:00,530 --> 00:42:01,960
Can't you see?

857
00:42:02,050 --> 00:42:03,170
Stop acting.

858
